::Hevn::
       He smiles at her mildly.  "Dear Blackstorm, if I couldn't defend 
myself, I wouldn't be much of a bodyguard now would I?"  He leans on the 
table resting his head in his hand while still looking her in the eye.  "Now 
then, don't worry about me.  Only worry about your happiness.  What would 
make you the happiest right now?"

--part1_a7.3170b51b.2be4b1b4_boundary
